This template creates a very concise reference citation to a specific book on the [[美国国家生物技术信息中心|NCBI Bookshelf]].

This template was created for {{tl|infobox disease}}.

==Usage==

<code><nowiki>{{NCBIBook2|NBKnnnn|Book Title}}</nowiki></code>

where "NBKnnnn" is the book id number, which is part of the canonical URL.  For example,

=== Examples ===

<code><nowiki>{{NCBIBook2|NBK1450|Amyotrophic Lateral Sclerosis Overview}}</nowiki></code>

produces: {{NCBIBook2|NBK1450|Amyotrophic Lateral Sclerosis Overview}}.  

Note that the title is optional, so

<code><nowiki>{{NCBIBook2|NBK1450}}</nowiki></code>

produces {{NCBIBook2|NBK1450}}.

